<p>As a super-sized traffic platform with over 5 billion downloads worldwide, TikTok has evolved from a entertainment social app into an indispensable core marketing channel for global businesses. However, with intensifying competition and continuously rising advertising costs, achieving efficient ROI returns has become the core challenge every international marketer must face.</p>
<p>This comprehensive guide systematically covers four key dimensions: <strong>Creative Design</strong>, <strong>Audience Targeting</strong>, <strong>Ad Optimization</strong>, and <strong>Data-Driven Iteration</strong>—providing actionable methodologies and cutting-edge trends for TikTok advertising success in 2024.</p>
