<h2>5. TikTok Advertising Trends &amp; Outlook 2024</h2>
<h3>5.1 Diversification of Creative Formats</h3>
<p><strong>TikTok Spark Ads (Native Ads)</strong> are becoming the choice for premium brands. By collaborating with real creators to embed ads in native content, commercial value is achieved while preserving authenticity. Data shows Spark Ads achieve <strong>2-3x higher engagement rates</strong> than traditional in-feed ads.</p>
